Designed for both Apple and Android phones, as well as most phone cases, this two-card holder seamlessly attaches to your device, providing convenience and style without the bulk of a traditional wallet. Installation is a breeze – simply peel back the adhesive protector and secure the wallet to the back of your phone. The magnetic disconnect feature allows you to effortlessly remove your wallet whenever you need to use a car mount or wireless charger, ensuring your on-the-go lifestyle remains uninterrupted.
One of the standout features of the Magnetic Phone Wallet is the ingenious edge design that catches the sticker backing, preventing the wallet from accidentally sliding off your phone and getting lost. This clever detail provides an extra layer of security and peace of mind for the user.
Upgrade your carry game with the Magnetic Phone Wallet – the perfect fusion of convenience, style, and functionality for those who demand efficiency and simplicity in their everyday essentials.

Meet the PocketMonkey® - Zootility’s original multi-tool. This small but mighty tool has 21 functions, fits in your wallet, and is compliant with all TSA rules. From opening bottles to adjusting screws, the PocketMonkey multi-tool helps you conquer everyday tasks easily. Made in the USA from heat-treated stainless steel, the PocketMonkey multi-tool won't bend, break, or rust.

PocketMonkey "Basic" comes with stenciled icons instead of black laser engraved markings. While less the text is visible, it's all the same great funcationality of the PocketMonkey Deluxe at a lower price.

The Headgehog™ is not your average comb. At 1mm thin and the size of a credit card, this comb is also a dynamic multi-tool featuring a bottle opener, phillips screwdriver, phone kickstand, money clip, and chip clip! The Headgehog™ is proudly made in the woods of Maine.

WildCard - the hyper thin pocket knife multi-tool. Made in the USA from heat-treated stainless steel, the WildCard is one of the easiest multi-tools for convenient storage due to it's ultra-thin design and patented FlyOff technology. The knife body also features built-in screwdrivers, pry bar, rulers, and bottle opener.
See how to open, close, attach, and remove your new blades in our Operating Manual.

Replacement blades for the WildCard™ and HT-420™ pocket knives. Each blade comes sharpened and ready for attachment. Made from heat-treated 420 Stainless Steel. These are not compatible with the Super Thin series (ST-2).
See how to open, close, attach, and remove your new blades in our Operating Manual

ST-2 is a Super Thin 440C stainless steel folding pocket knife with dual blade guards. Under all circumstances, the ST-2 is one of the easiest knives for convenient storage due to it's ultra-thin featherweight design and patented FlyOff technology. 
Made in the wood of Maine. See how to open, close, attach, and remove your new blades in our Operating Manual

Replacement blades for the ST-2 pocket knife. Each blade comes sharpened and ready for attachment. Made from heat-treated 440C Stainless Steel. Packaging includes innovative blade removal and insertion tool to simplify the removal process and protect the blade during attachment. See our tutorials explaining how to open, close, attach, and remove you new blades.

A great knife needs a great clip and this clip delivers. By utilizing space-age design, the clip is light and durable. Perfect for the person on the go; this stainless steel clip slides on easy and stays in place. Mounting hardware included. Made in the woods on Maine.

This set makes the perfect gift for the beer lover on the go! The Treasure Box comes with a Beer & Friends Wallet Opener and a Keyround® Crescent Key leather keychain. Useful and easy to carry with you everyday. Handmade and laser cut in the woods of Maine.

ST-1 is a super thin, ultra compact knife with keychain loop. The ST-1 is one of the easiest knives for convenient storage due to it's 0.125” low profile and patented FlyOff technology. 
Made in the woods of Maine.
See how to open, close, attach, and remove your new blades in our Operating Manual

The Hyper Thin Knife is the "World's Thinnest Pocket Knife". The patented FlyOff technology allows you to remove the blade quickly, without tools. The handle also includes a bottle opener, screwdriver, pry bar, and ruler.
See how to open, close, attach, and remove your new blades in our Operating Manual.

Meet the Grrilla - our bristle-free grill scraper. Use this to avoid those traditional harmful bristle brushes that can shed metal wires and pose a health risk. Grrilla is laser cut from stainless steel, creating a dishwasher safe grilling accessory. This modern scraper is compatible with almost any model of charcoal, propane, and campground grills.
For gas grills - turn grill on to burn off residue, turn gas off to scrape remaining residue. Charcoal Grills - scrape off residue before lighting charcoal.

Keep track of the requested doneness level for each of your guests, on the grill and on the serving platter. Each pack consists of 6 charms: 2 Rare, 2 Medium Rare, 1 Medium, and 1 Medium Well. These laser cut stainless steel charms are food and dishwasher safe.

This clean and modern piece easily transforms into home decor once you remove the brackets. The set comes with the Free Pong game board and 6 brackets.

Handmade and laser cut in the woods of Maine.

Introducing the "Fearless Crossbody" – the ultimate accessory for the modern, unstoppable woman. This sleek and stylish bag is designed to keep you organized, prepared, and confident as you conquer the world. Embrace your inner power and chase your dreams with the Fearless Crossbody by your side. Remember, you are not an imposter – you are a force to be reckoned with. Let this bag be your daily reminder to face challenges head-on and show the world what you're truly capable of. Be bold, be strong, be fearless.

Expertly crafted for versatility and style, the Fearless Crossbody is equally suited for your daily routine or venturing into the great outdoors. Made from upcycled plastic water bottles, its water-repellent fabric is both lightweight and durable, ensuring it stands up to life's adventures. The ingenious open-top dual pocket at the back of the bag, concealed against your body when carried, provides quick access to essentials like your phone, wallet, and keys. An additional outer zipper pocket adds extra organization for on-the-go convenience.

Opening the folded flap reveals a secure magnetic strip closure, spanning the entire width of the opening to keep your belongings safe. Crossbody bags have taken the world by storm, and the Fearless Crossbody is no exception, exuding both excitement and functionality. Meticulously laser-cut and handmade in Maine, this phenomenal bag is a testament to quality craftsmanship and an empowering companion for the unstoppable woman.

Product Name (Required): The Rift Wallet - Slim Metal RFID-Blocking
Product Description:
With the capacity to hold more than 10 credit and ID cards, as well as cash folded twice, the Rift Wallet's flexible design accommodates your needs without adding unnecessary bulk. The metal exterior not only exudes a sense of modern sophistication but also provides RFID protection, ensuring your sensitive card information remains safe from wireless skimming threats.
The innovative two-finger hole feature sets the Rift Wallet apart from the rest. Effortlessly push your cards up with two fingers, then pinch between the finger holes to "pop" the cards up and fan them out, allowing you to quickly and easily access the card you need.
Upgrade your carry game with the Rift Wallet – the perfect fusion of security, functionality, and sleek design for those who appreciate a minimalist approach to their everyday essentials.

Designed for both Apple and Android phones, as well as most phone cases, this two-card holder seamlessly attaches to your device, providing convenience and style without the bulk of a traditional wallet. Introducing our Custom Laser Engraved Wooden Wall Art: a stunning fusion of craftsmanship and personalization, transforming your cherished locations into one-of-a-kind decorative pieces for your home. The bright colors will make you stand out from the crowd, while the sailing rope shoulder strap adds a touch of nautical charm. Whether you're on the ocean or a lake, its over-the-shoulder crossbody style will keep you hands-free and ready for any adventure that comes your way. Join the movement towards sustainable fashion with the Calypso Crossbody, and look good while doing good for the planet.
